 {"title": "Guided scrolling format works for storytelling", "detail": "The vertical scroll layout walks buyers through content in a narrative sequence. Sellers can structure the Pod as a story: problem statement, solution overview, case studies, pricing, next steps. This format is more engaging than the folder-and-file approach that most deal rooms use. Buyers consume the content in context instead of jumping between disconnected documents."},
 {"title": "Strong engagement analytics with stakeholder tracking", "detail": "Trumpet tracks individual stakeholder activity across every section and document in the Pod. Reps see who visited, what they viewed, and how long they engaged. Real-time notifications fire when key contacts open the Pod. The analytics provide enough signal to time follow-ups and personalize outreach without drowning reps in data they won't use."},
