 {"title": "Smaller ecosystem and integration library", "detail": "As a UK-based company with a smaller customer base than US competitors, Trumpet's integration ecosystem is more limited. The core CRM integrations (Salesforce, HubSpot) work well, but niche integrations, marketplace apps, and third-party extensions are fewer. Teams with complex tech stacks may need workarounds for tools that Dock or GetAccept support natively."},
